202
00:15:19,859 --> 00:15:21,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢谢你响应了我的号召</font>

203
00:15:22,239 --> 00:15:24,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我等的就是阁下这种人才</font>

204
00:15:28,389 --> 00:15:30,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">比起拥有其他才能的人</font>

205
00:15:31,189 --> 00:15:33,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">阁下的到来让我最为喜悦！</font>

206
00:15:34,779 --> 00:15:39,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">陛下…竟会因我而感到喜悦…</font>

207
00:15:39,779 --> 00:15:43,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">大…大家都说我是死胖子</font>

208
00:15:43,039 --> 00:15:46,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说我是个为了食物白白浪费钱的傻子…</font>

209
00:15:47,359 --> 00:15:48,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">挺起胸膛吧</font>

210
00:15:48,709 --> 00:15:51,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">阁下这种不惜花费钱财也要追求美食的心</font>

211
00:15:51,169 --> 00:15:52,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">能拯救这个国家！</font>

212
00:15:53,519 --> 00:15:56,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">您所言当真？</font>

