00:15:56,579 --> 00:15:57,309
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是的</font>

214
00:15:57,389 --> 00:16:00,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你遍尝各国名食珍味所获得的知识</font>

215
00:16:00,979 --> 00:16:02,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将会成为救国的关键</font>

216
00:16:03,509 --> 00:16:06,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">请阁下务必祝我一臂之力</font>

217
00:16:07,139 --> 00:16:08,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好 好的！</font>

218
00:16:08,929 --> 00:16:11,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只要我的知识能派上用场</font>

219
00:16:11,209 --> 00:16:14,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那就请您尽情使用吧！</font>

220
00:16:16,659 --> 00:16:19,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">马尔库斯 按我们国家的习俗</font>

221
00:16:19,289 --> 00:16:20,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只要是为国家立了功 或者是未来可期的部下</font>

222
00:16:20,939 --> 00:16:22,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">国王便会赐予他一个姓氏吧</font>

223
00:16:23,169 --> 00:16:24,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是 是的</font>

224
00:16:24,429 --> 00:16:25,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">的确如此</font>

225
00:16:26,509 --> 00:16:29,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那邦乔 我赐予你「石冢」一姓</font>

226
00:16:30,989 --> 00:16:32,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在我的故国</font>

227
00:16:32,519 --> 00:16:35,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是某个「食物的无尽探求者和宣传者」的姓氏</font>

228
00:16:36,129 --> 00:16:38,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">期待你能有不负此姓的出色表现</font>

229
00:16:39,139 --> 00:16:44,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">由于相马国王在全国人民面前热烈迎接邦乔</font>

230
00:16:44,549 --> 00:16:49,259
