231
00:16:49,549 --> 00:16:53,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">此后 更多有才之士聚集到了艾尔孚利登</font>

232
00:16:56,139 --> 00:16:56,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">陛下</font>

233
00:16:57,009 --> 00:16:59,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">以上这三位皆是自荐而来</font>

234
00:16:59,639 --> 00:17:01,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">接下来这位则是他荐</font>

