00:17:03,259 --> 00:17:06,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">有请哈克亚·库欧米阁下上前</font>

236
00:17:06,709 --> 00:17:07,269
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是</font>

237
00:17:09,699 --> 00:17:12,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">此人在智慧方面崭露了才能</font>

238
00:17:12,619 --> 00:17:17,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其知识 记忆力 想必国内无人能出其右</font>

239
00:17:18,509 --> 00:17:21,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">既然是他荐 又是谁推荐了你呢？</font>

