00:17:53,259 --> 00:17:56,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那么 你就在王城的书库中当一个管理员吧</font>

251
00:17:56,979 --> 00:17:59,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给你管理员的权限 可以自由阅览</font>

252
00:18:00,249 --> 00:18:04,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那的确很好 我欣然领命…</font>

253
00:18:05,169 --> 00:18:08,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">直到刚才我都是这么想的</font>

254
00:18:09,149 --> 00:18:10,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在不这么想了？</font>

255
00:18:10,919 --> 00:18:12,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是的 我改主意了</font>

256
00:18:13,099 --> 00:18:14,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那你所求何职？</font>

257
00:18:17,359 --> 00:18:22,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如果可以 我想以我的智慧辅佐陛下成就霸业</font>

258
00:18:22,229 --> 00:18:24,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">霸业 口气不小啊</font>

259
00:18:24,889 --> 00:18:26,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且还要用智慧辅佐我…</font>

260
00:18:26,899 --> 00:18:28,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">他是想当军师吗</font>

261
00:18:30,769 --> 00:18:33,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你觉得自己有足够的才能做到这些？</font>

