00:18:59,409 --> 00:19:01,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">即便您还未察觉他的价值</font>

268
00:19:01,779 --> 00:19:04,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只是因为今后可能有用而留下他</font>

269
00:19:04,489 --> 00:19:06,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">作为王者便已经合格了</font>

