00:19:11,849 --> 00:19:13,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我原本是这么想的</font>

272
00:19:14,479 --> 00:19:16,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却没想到您会这样厚待他</font>

273
00:19:17,369 --> 00:19:19,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">算是让人欣慰的失算吧</font>

274
00:19:20,109 --> 00:19:25,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">陛下您很清楚如今这个国家最需要什么</font>

275
00:19:28,369 --> 00:19:33,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你也说了 我知道这个国家需要什么</font>

276
00:19:34,109 --> 00:19:37,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而你 对我来说会是必须的人才吗</font>

277
00:19:37,929 --> 00:19:40,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个希望陛下您亲自检验</font>

278
00:19:48,139 --> 00:19:49,059
