288
00:20:29,869 --> 00:20:35,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">此人拥有非常稀有的才能 能和鸟兽交流</font>

289
00:20:36,699 --> 00:20:40,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为检验真伪 我们带她去了马厩</font>

290
00:20:40,129 --> 00:20:43,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">她准确说出了马的健康状态和来历</font>

291
00:20:43,989 --> 00:20:46,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">据她本人说 是马自己告诉了她</font>

292
00:20:46,909 --> 00:20:50,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这能力堪称神异</font>

293
00:20:50,739 --> 00:20:55,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">妖狼族的国家在离艾尔孚利登遥远的北方啊</font>

294
00:20:55,599 --> 00:21:00,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是的 据我所知 应该没有妖狼族住在这个国家</font>

295
00:21:00,629 --> 00:21:03,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这么说 很可能是难民</font>

296
00:21:06,619 --> 00:21:11,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就算真是这样 也不改变唯才是举的方针</font>

297
00:21:11,739 --> 00:21:15,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">可问题在于怎么发挥她的才能</font>

298
00:21:15,679 --> 00:21:16,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那个…</font>

299
00:21:18,109 --> 00:21:18,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">国王陛下</font>

