00:21:19,229 --> 00:21:20,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么了？</font>

301
00:21:20,859 --> 00:21:26,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那个 这个 我…有话想对陛下说</font>

302
00:21:27,459 --> 00:21:29,319
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你有话想对我说？</font>

303
00:21:29,709 --> 00:21:31,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那就不用顾忌 说吧</font>

304
00:21:33,419 --> 00:21:34,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是这样…</font>

305
00:21:35,129 --> 00:21:35,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么了？</font>

306
00:21:36,049 --> 00:21:38,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你得大声一点 不然我听不见</font>

307
00:21:39,319 --> 00:21:41,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个 我…</font>

308
00:21:47,219 --> 00:21:49,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">知道了 我去你那边</font>

309
00:21:56,879 --> 00:21:59,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">行了 不用大声了</font>

310
00:22:00,089 --> 00:22:01,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">别紧张 说吧</font>

311
00:22:02,389 --> 00:22:05,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好的 是这样…</font>

312
00:22:09,989 --> 00:22:13,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一阵穿梭的疾风 穿越整个世界</font>

313
00:22:14,169 --> 00:22:18,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">连接不可能相遇的我们</font>

314
00:22:18,389 --> 00:22:22,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">展开没有人看得见的羽翼</font>

315
00:22:22,599 --> 00:22:26,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">找寻没有人看得见的奇迹</font>

316
00:22:26,529 --> 00:22:29,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">起飞吧</font>

317
00:22:35,429 --> 00:22:39,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">继续迷惘明日的方向</font>

318
00:22:39,619 --> 00:22:43,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">追求继续选择的勇气</font>

319
00:22:43,859 --> 00:22:47,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不曾怀疑天空有多蓝</font>

320
00:22:47,989 --> 00:22:52,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">希望我能毫不畏惧世事无常</font>

321
00:22:52,589 --> 00:22:54,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">比起将来的梦想</font>

322
00:22:54,809 --> 00:22:56,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">超越想象中的未来</font>

323
00:22:56,899 --> 00:23:00,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这般时光是如此美好</font>

324
00:23:01,199 --> 00:23:03,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我只想徜徉在其中</font>

325
00:23:03,379 --> 00:23:05,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和你共同度过现在</font>

326
00:23:05,429 --> 00:23:08,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要是能实现就好了</font>

327
00:23:08,799 --> 00:23:13,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">穿过湛蓝 绵延不断的天空</font>

328
00:23:13,739 --> 00:23:17,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将轮回的命运拉近身边</font>

329
00:23:17,429 --> 00:23:21,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">传达思念给紧握的手</font>

330
00:23:21,849 --> 00:23:26,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">仅仅希望这就是永远</font>

331
00:23:26,649 --> 00:23:28,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">即使现在只是幻影</font>

332
00:23:28,839 --> 00:23:31,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就算是在某人的梦境里</font>

333
00:23:31,029 --> 00:23:32,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一阵穿梭的疾风</font>

334
00:23:32,759 --> 00:23:37,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在抓住它 起飞吧</font>

